            "title": "1934 PRESSURIZATION",
            "text": "<p>illycaffè obtains a patent for the revolutionary pressurization system, still used by the company today to package its products: allowing coffee travel around the world whilst enhancing its aromas, maturing the flavors, and preserving its freshness.<br/><br/></p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": ""
          }
        },
