            "text": "<p>illycaffè industrializes, for the first time, pods, single-serving portions of ground and tampted coffee, that allows everyone to create the perfect espresso with ease: a radical innovation in the history of coffee, which paved the way for the internationalization of the company.</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": ""
          }
